'''BIEM (Bureau International des Sociétés Gérant les Droits d'Enregistrement et de Reproduction Mécanique)''' is an organisation coordinating [[statutory license]] agreements among different countries. BIEM is based in [[Neuilly-sur-Seine]], [[France]], and represents 55 societies, from 59 countries.<ref>{{Cite web|title = FAQs|url = http://www.biem.org/index.php?option=com_k2&view=item&layout=item&id=20&Itemid=442&lang=en|website = www.biem.org|accessdate = 2015-05-18}}</ref>

